 * @author Remco Bloemen <<a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="7a081f1719153a48">[email&#160;protected]</a>Ï€.com>
 * @dev This tries to block incoming ether to prevent accidental loss of Ether. Should Ether end up
